\ closers self-delimit: no space needed before ] or }
[ 1 2 3 4] . cr
{ :a 1} /a @ . cr

\ openers too: [ and { start their own token
[1 2 3 4 ] . cr
{:a 1 } /a @ . cr

\ fully glued on both sides
[1 2 3] . cr

\ two-char closers survive gluing: :] and )]
[:dup *:] 3 swap execute . cr
[( 1 2)] head-tail . . cr

\ the matrix typo from the field
[ 1 2 3 4] 2 2 matrix .

\ path predicates keep their brackets: no split inside [...]
{ :a { :n 1 } :b { :n 5 } } /*/n[.>2] select-values . cr

\ strings unaffected
"a]b{c" . cr
